Package: rllmdoc
Title: Unified llms.txt Generation for Quarto and R Package Projects
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates spec-compliant llms.txt and llms-full.txt files from
    Quarto website and book projects and R package (pkgdown) projects.
    Provides a unified interface that wraps native tooling, validates
    strictly against the llms.txt specification, and fails fast on missing
    metadata.
License: file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: quarto (>= 1.9.30)
Encoding: UTF-8
